                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/15959</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-06-13">June 13,
                            1940</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In view of this apparently indiscriminate bombing of Chungking without reference
                    to military objectives, should we call it to the attention of the Japanese
                    Government?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>F[<hi rend="smallcaps">ranklin</hi>] D. R[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                            >oosevelt</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
